The main taxonomy in the theme is tags, as it is the one listed under the title in every &ldquo;single&rdquo; page, but it&rsquo;s also possible to set any number of arbitrary taxonomies which will be listed in the side pane details section.
For example, in this site there&rsquo;s the taxonomies topic and series as defined in the config file.
[taxonomies] tag = &#39;tags&#39; topic = &#39;topics&#39; series = &#39;series&#39;

